title: Garmin Bluechart G2 Vision VUS030R - Southeast Caribbean
description:
The new Garmin G2 charts don't go into MapSource only to Garmin Mobile PC, but to use the full potential (e.g. embedded photographic images) you have to use it on a GPS that supports G2 Vision BlueCharts.
BlueChart G2 Vision maps are only sold on SD cards!!!


VUS030R - Southeast Caribbean

Covers the Caribbean from Haiti to Trinidad & Tobago, including Puerto
Rico and all of the Lesser Antilles. Also includes the Colombian and
Venezuelan coasts from Barranquilla, Colombia to the mouth of the
Orinoco River, including Lake Maracaibo and the Gulf of Paria.
